Title: Delectable Delicacies
Description:
Of course we will take care of the netherwhelps.

However, we might run low on snacks. The beetles close by are a delicious treat for the little ones. 

Can you bring me back some juicy beetle bits? Only the best for the little darlings!
ObjectivesText: Retrieve 10 Juicy Beetle Bits from Juicy Beetles in the Ruby Lifepools in Waking Shores.
